# CODEOWNERS - Automatic review assignment for Resonance
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# Each line is a file pattern followed by one or more owners.
# Order matters: later patterns override earlier ones.
# Teams use the format @org/team-name, users use @username
#
# NOTE: Using @cj-vana as default owner until GitHub teams are created.
# TODO: Replace @cj-vana with appropriate teams once organization is set up:
#   - @resonance-stream/maintainers (general maintainers)
#   - @resonance-stream/backend (Rust/API developers)
#   - @resonance-stream/frontend (React/TypeScript developers)
#   - @resonance-stream/devops (CI/CD and infrastructure)
#   - @resonance-stream/security (security-sensitive files)
#   - @resonance-stream/database (database and migrations)

